  title="History of Scrabble: From the Great Depression to 150 Million Sets"
  description="How an unemployed architect invented Scrabble during the Great Depression, got rejected repeatedly, and created one of history's best-selling board games."
  keywords="scrabble history, who invented scrabble, alfred butts scrabble, scrabble great depression, scrabble origin story, scrabble word finder, scrabble tiles, history of board games, scrabble inventor"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
